      <title>ubuntu下配置oh my zsh</title>
      <link href="/post/c4683e1f.html"/>
      <url>/post/c4683e1f.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装zsh"><a href="#安装zsh" class="headerlink" title="安装zsh"></a>安装zsh</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装-oh-my-zsh"><a href="#安装-oh-my-zsh" class="headerlink" title="安装 oh my zsh"></a>安装 oh my zsh</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#下载</span><br><span class="line">wget https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/raw/master/tools/install.sh  | sh</span><br><span class="line">#安装</span><br><span class="line">sh install.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="替换默认shell为Zsh"><a href="#替换默认shell为Zsh" class="headerlink" title="替换默认shell为Zsh"></a>替换默认shell为Zsh</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chsh -s /bin/zsh <span class="comment">#替换默认shell为zsh</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chsh -s /bin/bash <span class="comment">#替换回默认的shell</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>改完了注销&#x2F;重启下电脑才生效</strong></p><p>重启完后打开终端，使用</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看当前终端类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$SHELL</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 看到这样的输出就对了。</span></span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$SHELL</span>                             </span><br><span class="line">/bin/zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 简单配置<br>设置固定主题</p><ul><li>打开：<code> ~/.zshrc</code>（隐藏文件）</li><li>找到<code>ZSH_THEME=&quot;robbyrussell&quot;</code>,这里，已经设置了默认主题<code>robbyrussell</code>,若要修改主题请按此格式：<code>ZSH_THEME=&quot;主题名称&quot;</code>（我用了norm）</li><li>保存文件，更新配置文件 <code>source ~/.zshrc</code></li></ul><h3 id="安装插件"><a href="#安装插件" class="headerlink" title="安装插件"></a>安装插件</h3><p>1、自动补全 <a href="https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions">zsh-autosuggestions</a></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions $ZSH_CUSTOM/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2、语法高亮<a href="https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting">zsh-syntax-highlighting</a></p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git $ZSH_CUSTOM/plugins/zsh-syntax</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、引入插件"><a href="#3、引入插件" class="headerlink" title="3、引入插件"></a>3、引入插件</h3><p>下载完了以后打开 .zshrc 文件 放入plugins里面就可以。</p><p><strong>每个插件注意空格分隔 或者换行</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plugins=(git zsh-syntax-highlighting)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//或者这样</span><br><span class="line">plugins=(</span><br><span class="line">    git</span><br><span class="line">    zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br><span class="line">    zsh-autosuggestions</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后 source .&#x2F;.zshrc 就可以了</p>]]></content>
      
      
