      <title>conda和pip常用指令</title>
      <link href="/post/d4650996.html"/>
      <url>/post/d4650996.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>​记录一下常用的conda和pip指令~</p><h1 id="conda"><a href="#conda" class="headerlink" title="conda"></a>conda</h1><h2 id="查看版本号"><a href="#查看版本号" class="headerlink" title="查看版本号"></a>查看版本号</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="环境操作"><a href="#环境操作" class="headerlink" title="环境操作"></a>环境操作</h2><h3 id="创建虚拟环境"><a href="#创建虚拟环境" class="headerlink" title="创建虚拟环境"></a>创建虚拟环境</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda create -n your_env_name python=3.8</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看既存环境"><a href="#查看既存环境" class="headerlink" title="查看既存环境"></a>查看既存环境</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda env list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="进入环境"><a href="#进入环境" class="headerlink" title="进入环境"></a>进入环境</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">activate your_env_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="退出环境"><a href="#退出环境" class="headerlink" title="退出环境"></a>退出环境</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda deactivate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="删除环境"><a href="#删除环境" class="headerlink" title="删除环境"></a>删除环境</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda remove -n your_env_name --all</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="复制环境"><a href="#复制环境" class="headerlink" title="复制环境"></a>复制环境</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda create -n new_env_name --clone old_env_name </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="包操作"><a href="#包操作" class="headerlink" title="包操作"></a>包操作</h2><h3 id="查看安装的包"><a href="#查看安装的包" class="headerlink" title="查看安装的包"></a>查看安装的包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装包"><a href="#安装包" class="headerlink" title="安装包"></a>安装包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda install package_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="删除包"><a href="#删除包" class="headerlink" title="删除包"></a>删除包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda remove -n your_env_name package_name</span><br><span class="line">conda uninstall package_name</span><br><span class="line">conda remove package_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="更新包"><a href="#更新包" class="headerlink" title="更新包"></a>更新包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda update package_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="更新conda"><a href="#更新conda" class="headerlink" title="更新conda"></a>更新conda</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda update conda</span><br><span class="line">conda update anaconda</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看源"><a href="#查看源" class="headerlink" title="查看源"></a>查看源</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda config --show channels</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="pip"><a href="#pip" class="headerlink" title="pip"></a>pip</h1><h3 id="显示版本"><a href="#显示版本" class="headerlink" title="显示版本"></a>显示版本</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="包操作-1"><a href="#包操作-1" class="headerlink" title="包操作"></a>包操作</h2><h3 id="安装包-1"><a href="#安装包-1" class="headerlink" title="安装包"></a>安装包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install package_name              # 最新版本</span><br><span class="line">pip install package_name==1.0.4       # 指定版本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装requirements-txt文件中的所有包"><a href="#安装requirements-txt文件中的所有包" class="headerlink" title="安装requirements.txt文件中的所有包"></a>安装requirements.txt文件中的所有包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install -r requirements.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="将包导出requirements-txt"><a href="#将包导出requirements-txt" class="headerlink" title="将包导出requirements.txt"></a>将包导出requirements.txt</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip freeze &gt; requirements.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="更新包-1"><a href="#更新包-1" class="headerlink" title="更新包"></a>更新包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install --upgrade package_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="卸载包"><a href="#卸载包" class="headerlink" title="卸载包"></a>卸载包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip uninstall package_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="列出安装的包"><a href="#列出安装的包" class="headerlink" title="列出安装的包"></a>列出安装的包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看可升级的包"><a href="#查看可升级的包" class="headerlink" title="查看可升级的包"></a>查看可升级的包</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip list -o</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="升级pip"><a href="#升级pip" class="headerlink" title="升级pip"></a>升级pip</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install --upgrade pip</span><br><span class="line">python -m pip install --upgrade pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
